                            <h2 class="section-heading"> Steps to get Entry Certification in Business Analysis </h2>
                            <p style="display:inline;">Strengthen your expertise of business analysis processes and concepts with IIBA® certifications. Validate your expertise as a BA professional with the ECBA certification course and take advantage of wider, better job prospects. Not sure where to start with your ECBA certification training? Just follow these simple steps:</p><span class="view-more-link">.....</span> <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="view-more-link">View more</a>
