                                <div class="card">
                                    <div class="card-header"> <a class="card-link  collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#faq-heading-6-14">14. How do I join the class?</a> </div>
                                    <div id="faq-heading-6-14" class="collapse " data-parent="#faq-accordion-6">
